These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, cola, iced-tea
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, house, salsa
1. the fan of house is the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is between the fan of salsa and the person drinking cola##2
3. the person drinking milk is on the right of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | cola | iced-tea | milk |
| Music-Genre   | house     | country    | salsa   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: skydiving, puzzles, gardening
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, fisherman, police-officer
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the police-officer is between the security-guard and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | skydiving    | gardening        | puzzles |
| Job     | fisherman | police-officer | security-guard         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, soy-milk
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, goat, mouse
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the owner of the goat and the person drinking soy-milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | fanta | hot-chocolate     | soy-milk |
| Pet        | goat  | mouse | rabbit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, blues, salsa
3 different pets are kept: hamster, chinchilla, lizard
1. the fan of techno is the owner of the hamster##1
2. the fan of salsa is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the hamster##2
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | salsa     | techno |
| Pet           | chinchilla | lizard | hamster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, baking, filmmaking
3 different pets are kept: bird, lizard, snake
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
3. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the snake and the owner of the lizard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | baking | filmmaking     | chess |
| Pet     | snake    | bird | lizard    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, nigerian, russian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, skiing, badminton
1. the person who's sport is surfing is between the russian and the colombian##2
2. the colombian is the person who's sport is skiing##1
3. the nigerian is on the right of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | colombian  | nigerian   | russian        |
| Sport         | skiing | surfing | badminton |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: apple, watermelon, pomegranate
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, japanese, polish
1. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person eating apple##1
2. the spanish is between the person eating pomegranate and the japanese##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | watermelon  | apple  | pomegranate |
| Nationality   | japanese | spanish | polish     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, spy, musical
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, egyptian, thai
1. the person watching spy movies is the thai##1
2. the egyptian is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching musical movies##2
3. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | fantasy  | spy  |
| Nationality   | japanese | egyptian | thai |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, volleyball, snowboarding
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, taxi, motorbike
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person driving the roller is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person driving the taxi##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Sport       | snowboarding | cricket | volleyball  |
| Transport   | motorbike    | roller        | taxi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
