The people use 3 different means of transport: van, boat, jet-ski
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the software-developer##1
2. the architect is between the person driving the jet-ski and the videographer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Job         | software-developer | architect | videographer |
| Transport   | jet-ski     | van    | boat |

