.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, iced-tea
There 3 different types of food: potato, orange, spinach
1. the person eating spinach is between the person drinking tea and the person eating potato##2
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | tea | soy-milk      | iced-tea      |
| Food       | orange  | spinach | potato |

