.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, techno, hip-hop
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, climbing, skateboarding
1. the fan of techno is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's sport is climbing##2
3. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | house | techno   | hip-hop   |
| Sport         | climbing | skateboarding | surfing |

