.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-19::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, fantasy, western
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, d&b, rock
1. the person watching western movies is between the fan of salsa and the person watching scientific movies##2
2. the fan of rock is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | western | fantasy |
| Music-Genre   | d&b    | rock | salsa   |

