.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, coffee, lemonade
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, r&b, pop
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking lemonade and the fan of r&b##2
3. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Beverage      | lemonade | coffee   | mirinda |
| Music-Genre   | pop  | d&b | r&b   |

 